  "title": "Secondary/JC Tuition Teacher",
  "description": "<p>We are a small, fast-growing tuition centre in Singapore built for the new generation of education - high-quality teaching, strong student outcomes, and modern outreach (social media, live teaching, trials). We believe great tutors are not just teachers, but communicators, mentors, and builders. If you want to grow with the company, build your own student base, and be rewarded for performance, this role is for you.</p><p><br />Who We’re Looking For</p><ul><li>Undergraduates / Graduates from any discipline with excellent academic track records</li><li>Strong relevant subject mastery (Secondary / JC level)</li><li>Willing to prepare lesson materials and grow students from scratch</li><li>Excellent interpersonal skills, confident public speaker and able to connect with students</li><li>Prior teaching experience, and proficiency in LaTeX is highly advantageous</li><li>Driven, enthusiastic, caring and excited by performance-based growth and upside</li><li>Comfortable with being on-camera for social media-based outreach (TikTok LIVE, short videos, live teaching)</li><li>Willing to offer trial/free lessons as part of outreach</li><li>Open to feedback and fast iteration</li></ul><p><br />What We Offer</p><ul><li>Highly competitive compensation package</li><li>Flexible teaching schedules</li></ul><p><br />Ideal for</p><ul><li>Ambitious undergraduates or postgraduates</li><li>Ex-MOE teachers who want higher upside</li><li>Educators who want their effort to directly translate into income growth</li></ul>",
